OpenGL C++ Projects

*Instructions*

1.  Open project in Visual Studios
2.  Right click on the project in the solution explorer
3.  Follow directions Below:
  1. Click C++ Additional Indludes Directories
  2. Configuration Properties 
    > 
    C/C++/General/Additional 
    Include Directories
  3. Paste Path of Includes folder
  4. Click Linker and do the same for Libs folder
  5. Configuration Properties 
    > 
    Linker/General/Additional 
    Library Directories
  6. Click Input (edit) paste the following:
     opengl32.lib 
     glfw3.lib
     glew32s.lib
4. Project is now Ready
